descriptionHTML:
YSAR fancy skull watch face collection is made for most stylish smartwatch users.To get our fashionable skull watch face means that you have modern style and exceptional taste. Features are simple as much attention was paid to modern and elegant design.

Features:
- Hours, minutes
- Ambient mode

Functions:
- Skull color choice
- Arrows color choice
- Ambient mode color choice

You will see our application right after you download from store. YSAR watch faces do not require much energy, so your smartwatch will operate for almost the same period of time as usual.

Watch Faces by YSAR design are absolute symbols of style. Watch faces by YSAR Design are compatible with both round and square android wear smartwatches: Moto 360, Asus ZenWatch, LG G Watch R, LG G Watch, LG Watch Urbane, Samsung Gear Live, Sony Smartwatch 3, Huawei Watch etc..

Check out our watch faces with different features and designs: https://play.google.com/store/apps/developer?id=YSAR+Design

Please, rate, share and write comments, because we want to improve our watch faces and satisfy your needs.
comments: Settings Settings doesn't stick in its application. And this watchface appears darker on watch than it's photos in play store
Good but needs improving. Good app but I would give it ***** if I had the option to put a widget for watch battery and date ect.
Unusual watchface Like this watch face, new update works fine for me. Recommended for anyone who wants something unusual
Latest update ruined the watch face The latest update changes the look of  the watch face in "sleep" mode. It is ugly! I am uninstalling it. Don't waste your money.
